						<summary>

						<p>This inscription seems to registers the gift of taxes collected from the village Tiruppuṭkuḻi by a certain Kāñjikkuṟivaradarāja for burning lamps and food offerings in the temple of Pōreṟṟu nāyiṉār, for the merit of Ellamarasa.</p>						

						</summary>
